== 公路 ==
[[File:Hokkaido_Expwy_near_Eniwa.jpg|thumb]]的[[道央自动车道|道央自动车道]]]]
{{main|日本高速公路|:ja:日本の道路|l2=日本公路}}

尽管国土狭小，日本的道路总长度居世界第五位<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2085rank.html | title=Rank Order - Roadways CIA World factbook | accessdate=2013-12-10 | archive-date=2017-09-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170907162530/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2085rank.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，國家[[高速公路|高速公路]]长达7920公里<ref>{{cite web | url= http://www.mlit.go.jp/road/road_e/pdf/ROAD2012web.pdf | title= Roads in Japan 2012 | accessdate= 2013-08-01 | format= pdf | deadurl= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140801064758/http://www.mlit.go.jp/road/road_e/pdf/ROAD2012web.pdf | archivedate= 2014-08-01 }}</ref>。連接[[本州|本州]]和[[四國|四國]]的[[明石海峽大橋|明石海峽大橋]]是世界上最長的[[吊橋|吊橋]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.jr-central.co.jp/company/company/achievement/transportation/index.html|title=JR Central Japan Website|accessdate=2013-12-11|archive-date=2014-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140311211949/http://english.jr-central.co.jp/company/company/achievement/transportation/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="fc2web">{{cite web |url=http://whhh.fc2web.com/ktx/hikaku.html |title=KTX vs 新幹線 徹底比較 |publisher=Whhh.fc2web.com |accessdate=2013-08-10 |archive-date=2016-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160824122806/http://whhh.fc2web.com/ktx/hikaku.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根据日本国家高速道路建设协会的统计，每日平均有441万辆车使用高速公路，平均行驶距離為43.7公里<ref>{{cite news|first=Kazuaki|last=Nagata|publisher=The Japan Times|date=December 16, 2008|url=http://search.japantimes.co.jp/cgi-bin/nn20081216i1.html|title=A highway system that ever exacts toll|accessdate=2013-12-13|archive-date=2008-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081216083358/http://search.japantimes.co.jp/cgi-bin/nn20081216i1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

日本的国家高速公路收費較高，經[[东名高速公路|东名高速公路]]从[[东京|东京]]到[[名古屋|名古屋]]的路程需要7650[[日圓|日圓]]<ref>{{cite web | url= http://global.c-nexco.co.jp/cn/toll/toll_tokyo.html#nagoya | title= 从东京、成田国际机场方向出发 | author= 中日本高速道路株式会社 | accessdate= 2013-08-01 | archive-date= 2017-03-18 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170318213701/http://global.c-nexco.co.jp/cn/toll/toll_tokyo.html#nagoya | dead-url= no }}</ref>。

== 空運 ==
[[File:130224_Tokyo_International_Airport02s3.jpg|thumb]]
{{see also|日本機場列表}}
[[日本|日本]]的航空运输业相当发达，[[東京國際機場|東京國際機場]]（羽田機場）和[[成田國際机场|成田國際机场]]的客货吞吐量均居世界前列，其中[[東京国际机场|東京国际机场]]（羽田機場）2012年的旅客吞吐量為[[全球機場客運吞吐量列表|亞洲第二]]，達到6782.5萬人次<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.aci.aero/Data-Centre/Monthly-Traffic-Data/Passenger-Summary/12-months | title=Monthly Traffic Data: Passenger Summary (12 months) | accessdate=2013-11-19 | archive-date=2018-03-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180309054651/http://www.aci.aero/Data-Centre/Monthly-Traffic-Data/Passenger-Summary/12-months | dead-url=no }}</ref>，是世界上最繁忙的机场之一<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.airports.org/cda/aci_common/display/main/aci_content07_c.jsp?zn=aci&cp=1-5-212-218-222_666_2__ |title=Passenger Traffic 2011 Preliminary |accessdate=2013-12-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120219174500/http://www.airports.org/cda/aci_common/display/main/aci_content07_c.jsp?zn=aci&cp=1-5-212-218-222_666_2__ |archivedate=2012-02-19 }}</ref>。在2013年机场服务质量排名中，羽田机场也位列世界第二<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldairportawards.com/Awards_2013/beststaff.htm |title=World's Best Airport Staff Service Awards |accessdate=2013-12-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130630162833/http://www.worldairportawards.com/Awards_2013/beststaff.htm |archivedate=2013-06-30 }}</ref>，航班晚点率全球最低<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.theage.com.au/executive-style/business-travel/worlds-most-ontime-airports-20090909-fhfr.html | location=Melbourne | work=The Age | first=Jeff | last=Koyen | title=World's most on-time airports | date=9 September 2009 | accessdate=2013-12-13 | archive-date=2012-11-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106141755/http://www.theage.com.au/executive-style/business-travel/worlds-most-ontime-airports-20090909-fhfr.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，而且是全球衛生情況最佳的機場<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldairportawards.com/Awards_2013/category.htm |title=Airport Award winners - by Category |accessdate=2013-12-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130829092810/http://www.worldairportawards.com/Awards_2013/category.htm |archivedate=2013-08-29 }}</ref>。日本的三大航空公司——[[日本航空|日本航空]]、[[全日空|全日空]]、[[天馬航空|天馬航空]]，是日本空中交通的重要标志。

日本全國共有175個機場<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/ja.html | title=CIA Factbook | accessdate=2013-12-13 | archive-date=2007-06-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070612201800/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/ja.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，全球排名第33<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2053rank.html?countryname=Japan&countrycode=ja&regionCode=eas&rank=33#ja33 | title=COUNTRY COMPARISON :: AIRPORTS | publisher=[[中情局|中情局]] | accessdate=2013-12-13 | archive-date=2020-05-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200526055324/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2053rank.html?countryname=Japan&countrycode=ja&regionCode=eas&rank=33#ja33 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
